                        <h3 class="mb-2">When we serve, we reflect God’s love</h3>
                        <p>As we reflect on this teaching, we are reminded that serving with love is not about seeking recognition or reward, but about responding to the needs of others with humility and compassion. When we serve, we reflect God’s love, not just through grand gestures, but through simple, everyday acts of kindness and care. This is how we live out our school motto: Learn, Love, and Serve. In learning, we grow in our understanding of God’s love; in loving, we serve others with a heart full of compassion; and in serving, we transform our community and the world around us.</p>


